59e')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_259e" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>"Every conviction is a prison" ---- Nietzsche</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_259e"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_259e" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_259e')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_259e" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_259e')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_259e" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ay/rationality_quotes_june_2010/259e?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_259e" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_259e')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_259e class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_259e" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_253a" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_253a" class="parent"><a name="253a" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_253a" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_253a" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_253a" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/cupholder/">cupholder</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">12 June 2010 12:18:25PM</span><span class="votes " >4 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_253a'] = ['3 points', '4 points', '5 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_253a')">[+] (1 child)</a></div><div id="display_t1_253a" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_253a" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/cupholder/">cupholder</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">12 June 2010 12:18:25PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_253a'>4 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_253a'] = ['3 points', '4 points', '5 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_253a')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_253a" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>Do not ask whether a statement is true until you know what it means.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>— <a href="http://www-history.mcs.st-and.ac.uk/Biographies/Bishop.html" rel="nofollow">Errett Bishop</a></p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_253a"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_253a" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_253a')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_253a" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_253a')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_253a" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ay/rationality_quotes_june_2010/253a?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_253a" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_253a')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_253a class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_253a" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_253a" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_253a" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_25wg" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_25wg" class="parent"><a name="25wg" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_25wg" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_25wg" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_25wg" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">18 June 2010 12:35:28PM</span><span class="votes " >1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_25wg'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_25wg')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_25wg" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_25wg" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">18 June 2010 12:35:28PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_25wg'>1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_25wg'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_25wg')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_25wg" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Bad advice.</p>

<p>I do not want to understand all untrue statements. Not only is there an opportunity cost associated with thinking or learning, understanding false statements can bias your brain in undesirable directions.</p>

<p>There are times (say, you know an expert you trust on the subject) when you can establish with acceptable confidence that a statement is not true. In such cases it is often better to not bother giving the false statement another thought.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_25wg"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_25wg" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_25wg')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_25wg" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_25wg')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_25wg" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ay/rationality_quotes_june_2010/25wg?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_25wg" href="#253a" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_25wg" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_25wg')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_25wg class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_25wg" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_24k7" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_24k7" class="parent"><a name="24k7" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_24k7" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_24k7" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_24k7" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/khafra/">khafra</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">09 June 2010 11:08:22AM</span><span class="votes " >2 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_24k7'] = ['1 point', '2 points', '3 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_24k7')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_24k7" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author">