m/user/Zubon/">Zubon</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">03 June 2010 01:19:57AM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_23lh'>8 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_23lh'] = ['7 points', '8 points', '9 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_23lh')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_23lh" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
