  <p>You see things; and you say, 'Why?' But I dream things that never were; and I say, 'Why not?'</p>
</blockquote>

<p>-- G.B.S.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_24gv"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_24gv" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_24gv')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_24gv" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_24gv')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_24gv" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ay/rationality_quotes_june_2010/24gv?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_24gv" href="#24gr" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_24gv" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_24gv')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_24gv class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_24gv" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_24gv" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_24gv" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_25wm" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_25wm" class="parent"><a name="25wm" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_25wm" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_25wm" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_25wm" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">18 June 2010 01:05:08PM</span><span class="votes " >1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_25wm'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_25wm')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_25wm" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_25wm" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">18 June 2010 01:05:08PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_25wm'>1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_25wm'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class