ck="return hidecomment('t1_252z')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_252z" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Not only to recognize my mistakes, but to actually speak outloud about them frequently has given me great strengh in doing it in questions that really matter. 
