#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_23ds')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_23ds" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>It's very Philosophy 101; you can get more in-depth info online. But it does provide an entry into a variety of topics, and some of the jokes are real zingers.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_23ds"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_23ds" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_23ds')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_23ds" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_23ds')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_23ds" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ay/rationality_quotes_june_2010/23ds?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_23ds" href="#23c1" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_23ds" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_23ds')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_23ds class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_23ds" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2380" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2380" class="parent"><a name="2380" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2380" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2380" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2380" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Houshalter/">Houshalter</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">01 June 2010 08:29:38PM</span><span class="votes " >14 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2380'] = ['13 points', '14 points', '15 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2380')">[+] (29 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2380" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2380" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Houshalter/">Houshalter</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">01 June 2010 08:29:38PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2380'>14 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2380'] = ['13 points', '14 points', '15 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2380')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2380" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
