turn hidecomment('t1_2389')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2389" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Hate spinach, love ice cream, love mother. What's so difficult?</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2389"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2389" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2389')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2389" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2389')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2389" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ay/rationality_quotes_june_2010/2389?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_2389" href="#2385" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2389" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2389')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2389 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2389" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_2389" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_2389" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_23h6" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_23h6" class="parent"><a name="23h6" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_23h6" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_23h6" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_23h6" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/SilasBarta/">SilasBarta</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">02 June 2010 08:50:50PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " >3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_23h6'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_23h6')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_23h6" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_23h6" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/SilasBarta/">SilasBarta</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">02 June 2010 08:50:50PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_23h6'>3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_23h6'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_23h6')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_23h6" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>What's so difficult?</p>
</blockquote>

<p>For you, understanding what was asked.  The question is not, "what will happen?"  The question is, "What <em>information</em> do you need in order to know which outcome will happen?"</p>

<p>Can someone explain why the parent is upvoted?  Is everyone just assuming that the Bateson quote is just a sarcastic, roundabout way of asking what will happen?</p>

<p><strong>ETA:</strong> In case you weren't aware, cousin_it is <a href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ay/rationality_quotes_june_2010/23f5">not joking</a> with his comment.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_23h6"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_23h6" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_23h6')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_23h6" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_23h6')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_23h6" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ay/rationality_quotes_june_2010/23h6?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_23h6" href="#2389" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_23h6" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_23h6')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_23h6 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_23h6" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_23d6" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_23d6" class="parent"><a name="23d6" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_23d6" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_23d6" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_23d6" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Eliezer_Yudkowsky/">Eliezer_Yudkowsky</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">02 June 2010 10:12:01AM</span><span class="votes " >4 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_23d6'] = ['3 points', '4 points', '5 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_23d6')">[+] (13 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_23d6" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_23d6" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Eliezer_Yudkowsky/">Eliezer_Yudkowsky</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">02 